An instance of the fcos3d\_r101-caffe-dcn\_fpn\_head-gn\_8xb2-1x\_nus-mono3d model, which is a FCOS3D ([https://arxiv.org/abs/2104.10956](https://arxiv.org/abs/2104.10956)) monocular 3D detector. It was trained with the default train configuration (with the exceptions of the epochs which were set to 1 \-this modification was made due to time constraints, the full training would have taken over 72 hours-) provided by mmdetection3D on the entire nuScenes dataset. This camera only  model was used because I was not able to find the lidar data of the nuisances dataset on the HPC storage.
